### Next JS portfolio Website and Blog
Here we are creating a next JS portfolio site and a blog page which is being powered by Sanity and user interface is built from a **Acentry UI**, **Framer motion** for making it easier to program.

Concept: 
 - Blog -  FreeCode Camp blog page Next JS and back end is Sonny Sangha sanity and next JS blog.
 - Portfolio - Sonny Sangha portfolio with sanity (major Inspiration), java mastery secondary.

Features:
- Light and Dark Interface
- Floating nav bar
- Grid Background (user interface)
- Responsive Design
- Typewriter effect
- Framer motion
- Sanity backend to keep the and release based on requirement.


Sections included:
- Header - includes float Navbar, Social and a logo Data Grid(blog name)
- Hero Section - Giving an introduction. (rounded image, with blue and )
